Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:26.06,Main,Girl walla,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:29.45,Main,Girl 2 walla,0000,0000,0000,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:32.47,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Estou tendo muita sorte!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:37.04,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Esse é o efeito do Safado Sortudo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.64,Flashback,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ofuscante!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.64,Flashback_Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Q-Que habilidade incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.85,Flashback_Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Você é a melhor, Mestra!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:45.84,Flashback,Olivia,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ofuscante!
