Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.95,0:23:24.84,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Teatro da Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.69,0:23:30.16,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Irmão querido...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:34.10,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,V-Você voltou cedo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:36.10,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Alice? O que estava fazendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:38.64,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eu estava...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.91,0:23:41.39,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Esticando seus lençóis!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:42.98,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Tá mais bagunçado que antes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:47.55,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Mas tudo bem, já vou dormir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.04,0:23:50.35,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Hã? Querido irmão?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.35,0:23:53.52,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Bom, somos irmãos...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.52,0:23:56.78,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Quando éramos crianças,\Nera comum dormirmos juntos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.78,0:23:59.50,Main,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sim, verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.02,0:24:06.97,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mas a Alice é minha irmã...
